<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">谢邀。<br><br>《三国演义》前面几集的袁绍。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/472a890908fb00cf13f8d69f11672da0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="448" data-rawheight="336" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="448" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/472a890908fb00cf13f8d69f11672da0_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="448" data-rawheight="336" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="448" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/472a890908fb00cf13f8d69f11672da0_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/472a890908fb00cf13f8d69f11672da0_b.jpg"><br>其实和周瑜都是由洪宇宙饰演的。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/b99ea8c7064d28e64da61abf94d4a0ff_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="746" data-rawheight="474" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="746" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/b99ea8c7064d28e64da61abf94d4a0ff_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="746" data-rawheight="474" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="746" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/b99ea8c7064d28e64da61abf94d4a0ff_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/b99ea8c7064d28e64da61abf94d4a0ff_b.jpg"><br>我看了很多年才发现，他们居然是同一个人。<br><br>彩蛋：美周郎的小拇指甲盖很长。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e2415982e73b64a176d739ae6c7b7936_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="477" data-rawheight="348" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="477" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/e2415982e73b64a176d739ae6c7b7936_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="477" data-rawheight="348" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="477" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/e2415982e73b64a176d739ae6c7b7936_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/e2415982e73b64a176d739ae6c7b7936_b.jpg">


