<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">咕噜（《魔戒》）<br><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/61b9a639d64aca930d38e13a07a86879_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="292" class="content_image" width="400"><br>凯撒（《猩球崛起》）<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/07b401d498c612544b5dd54b0d684406_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/07b401d498c612544b5dd54b0d684406_r.jpg"><br>金刚（《金刚》）<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/ecdb5953fe0e08972dfcb73f25855626_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/ecdb5953fe0e08972dfcb73f25855626_r.jpg"><br>阿道克船长（《丁丁历险记》）<br><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/f50ec27e254e8b84d17e1ecbd791313c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/f50ec27e254e8b84d17e1ecbd791313c_r.jpg"><br><br>偶尔也以真脸出现：<br>特斯拉的助手艾伦（《致命魔术》）<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/11bb8434af7afa00e7e509e194d4062a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="399" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/11bb8434af7afa00e7e509e194d4062a_r.jpg"><br>并且演过一些人类历史上的伟大人物：<br>爱因斯坦（虽然其实不怎么像）（《爱因斯坦与艾丁顿》）<br><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/48eb9c49f33c2cdd64db9b71c9f3ad7b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/48eb9c49f33c2cdd64db9b71c9f3ad7b_r.jpg"><br><br>梵高（《艺术的力量·梵高》）<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/50d2a0f532125068647b3a4f0bd105fe_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="720" data-rawheight="575" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="720" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/50d2a0f532125068647b3a4f0bd105fe_r.jpg"><br>但大多数时候……<br><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/13eb053b415ac3a36980c2e14169ac64_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="401" data-rawheight="455" class="content_image" width="401"><br>甚至是……<br><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/392b880cda315cf7b869d18d17baae49_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="597" class="content_image" width="400"><br>向地球上最伟大的动作捕捉演员<br>Andy Serkis<br>致敬
